{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 21 shows the end-to-end latency per request with and without the earlyexit branch.",
    "In many settings, the median end-to-end latency in the case of early-exit DNN variants is lower than that of the case without the early-exit branch.",
    "However, we observe that this does not always indicate that the early-exit technique offers low end-to-end latency.",
    "This is because the 16 DNN variants have different latency profiles with and without the early-exit branch.",
    "The early-exit DNN variants have higher latency profile values due to the additional time spent at the first early-exit branch."
  ]
}